Walk around the room

high_descs: Turn around to head to the counter on the left of the sink in the kitchen.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn around to reach the dining table.
Cut the lettuce on the table with the knife.
Look down to face the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Look up to face the lettuce.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the table.
Turn around to walk to the fridge on the left.
Cool the lettuce in the fridge and take it out.
Turn right to reach the sink counter top.
Put the slice of lettuce on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled slice of lettuce on the sink counter top.

high_descs: Turn back and walk towards the sink which is in the end of the room
Take a knife from the back side of the laptop
Turn back and walk towards a table
Cut a lettuce in to pieces
Hold the knife in front of the dining table
Put the knife on the bottom right of the dining table
Head towards a lettuce on the dining table
Take a piece of lettuce from the cut lettuce
Turn towards back and reach the fridge
Open the door and put the lettuce piece inside it and close the door. After few seconds open the door and take the lettuce piece out and again close the fridge door
Turn right and walk towards sink
Put the lettuce on the bottom left of the sink top
anns.task_desc: Put the lettuce on the bottom left of the sink top
